{"tid":1985485,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"地盤工施襲案 離職警拒任控方證人","createTime":"2020-04-23T07:31:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-23T08:57:48.000Z","uid":25558,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e47440c647b477c81a3e7a976e068b03b80be652","tid":1985485,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T07:31:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200423/JTYFUJMHQDG56LJP3S4YJLZFJQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200423%2FJTYFUJMHQDG56LJP3S4YJLZFJQ%2F&d=7FLALsszV4LuAMmN05fc6slSugA1I0CCabXjLbCjl00%3D&h=a31c114a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200423%2FJTYFUJMHQDG56LJP3S4YJLZFJQ%2F&h=5dbcc9eb\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200423/JTYFUJMHQDG56LJP3S4YJLZFJQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n地盤工施襲案 離職警拒任控方證人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200423/large/1587573261_a1a1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200423%2Flarge%2F1587573261_a1a1.jpg&h=55ac2173&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n東區法院<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】市民去年9月中旬到港島區「自由行」，其後發生警民衝突。有地盤工人被指當日在北角以鐵枝毆打一名七旬漢的右臂，事後被落案起訴。涉案地盤工人昨在東區法院否認普通襲擊罪，案件6月1日開審，審期預計兩天，他續准保釋。庭上透露，當天拘捕被告的警員已離職，並拒任控方證人出庭作供。辯方表示，擬傳召他作證。<br />\n<br />\n控罪指被告梁國偉（39歲）去年9月15日在北角英皇道益新洋樓外襲擊顏加星（72歲）。據了解，控方指事主當時正與在場記者交涉，其間被告突然襲擊事主。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n辯方擬傳召出庭<br />\n<br />\n控方透露，案中拘捕被告的警員已經離職，並拒絕出庭。該名警員已經不在控方證人列表上，控方不會傳召他作供。惟辯方表示，打算傳召該離職警出庭，以質疑另外兩名警員證人在案中所為，與他們所供述的有出入。辯方亦會爭議被告是否真的有襲擊事主。<br />\n<br />\n辯方指被告很可能會作供，另有兩名案發前半小時至一小時在場拍攝片段及相片的人士作為辯方證人，但拍片者沒目擊事發經過。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：ESCC2670/19"},{"pid":"e7c4a122ecda7a567b945ba6ff73be8c05c63c89","tid":1985485,"uid":231583,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T07:33:18.000Z","msg":"惟辯方表示，打算傳召該離職警出庭，以質疑另外兩名警員證人在案中所為，與他們所供述的有出入。辯方亦會爭議被告是否真的有襲擊事主。<br />\n<br />\n隻離職狗會咁做分分鐘被消失......"},{"pid":"4fbb16949226ddc84a7bf90c8e2354ff5f081bc9","tid":1985485,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T07:33:52.000Z","msg":"咁係咪好大機會無罪䆁放？"},{"pid":"c144b219e8e99f73b20254f21f24772e7ed2287c","tid":1985485,"uid":36164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T07:34:47.000Z","msg":"回頭是岸"},{"pid":"4c8de4c593dc8fc8792203778e0d00b77018ca43","tid":1985485,"uid":105976,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T07:34:56.000Z","msg":"證明冇白警  有都辭左職"},{"pid":"2d595e9740462f4e87a6545d63c550e0049db543","tid":1985485,"uid":223780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T07:35:31.000Z","msg":"佢做唔做都死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1682de271baaeaab7cfa0ef7fa242c58351454b","tid":1985485,"uid":210140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T07:36:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf499664268b5056a98431010f8232aaf89233eb","tid":1985485,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T07:38:15.000Z","msg":"即係單案係手足私了福建幫？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9675558ce3a5025b9ca89a78b0fe8a1203ee2151","tid":1985485,"uid":109570,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T07:39:29.000Z","msg":"其實係大陸公安？"},{"pid":"0c7d9f485d501fe7c97a5ae3636584cac21e1430","tid":1985485,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T07:40:31.000Z","msg":"佢走得就唔會做證人"},{"pid":"47d5306d95edb476e4e87c860783c7c624e98d79","tid":1985485,"uid":56624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9675558ce3a5025b9ca89a78b0fe8a1203ee2151","tid":1985485,"uid":109570,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"